              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A high purity germanium detector of 23%",
                "relative efficiency and resolution of 2 keV at 1.332",
                "MeV was placed at 90 degree to the beam direction."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP",
                "MWPC",
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The focal plane detector system",
                "consisted of a 200 mm x 60 mm position-sensitive",
                "multiwire proportional counter followed by a 180 mm",
                "deep split-anode ionization chamber with an area of",
                "120 mm x 35 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The fusion cross sections were obtained by summing up",
                "the contributions from the dominant channels,",
                "corresponding to evaporation of up to seven nucleons."
              ]
            }
          ],
